#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:2 44527a2bce5441678202fb3087261966
msgid "共存"
msgstr "Coexistence"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:17 bf68a8ade0714bfb86b39e01f6737072
msgid "Wi-Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存时，支持哪些模式？"
msgstr "Which modes are supported when Wi-Fi and ESP-BLE-MESH coexist?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:19 eb94c8acfd7e426b8aaf413d952d789b
msgid "目前，只有 Wi-Fi STA 模式支持共存。"
msgstr "Currently, coexistence is supported only in Wi-Fi STA mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:24 f95feef5e2804ec3bd2470253866313d
msgid "Wi-Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存时，为什么 Wi-Fi 吞吐量很低？"
msgstr "Why is Wi-Fi throughput very low when Wi-Fi and ESP-BLE-MESH coexist?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:26 d931b4363eaf4a27a065e1d6548ed72c
msgid "未搭载 PSRAM 的 ESP32-DevKitC 开发板，Wi-Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存可以正常运行，但是吞吐率较低。当 Wi-Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存时，搭载 PSRAM 的 ESP32-DevKitC 速率可以稳定在 1 Mbps 以上。"
msgstr "On an ESP32-DevKitC development board without PSRAM, Wi-Fi and ESP-BLE-MESH coexistence can run normally, but the throughput is low. When Wi-Fi and ESP-BLE-MESH coexist, the throughput of an ESP32-DevKitC equipped with PSRAM can remain stable above 1 Mbps."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:28 3373c929d13b43e187a6b90591ffa1bc
msgid "应使能 menuconfig 中的一些配置来支持 PSRAM:"
msgstr "Some configurations in menuconfig should be enabled to support PSRAM:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:30 03535db9026c499f858d285e1d24a8b8
msgid "``ESP32-specific --> Support for external,SPI-connected RAM --> Try to allocate memories of Wi-Fi and LWIP...``"
msgstr "``ESP32-specific --> Support for external,SPI-connected RAM --> Try to allocate memories of Wi-Fi and LWIP...``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:31 5398a668dbb74aa2b47ca5128be6669a
msgid "``Bluetooth --> Bluedriod Enable --> BT/BLE will first malloc the memory from the PSRAM``"
msgstr "``Bluetooth --> Bluedriod Enable --> BT/BLE will first malloc the memory from the PSRAM``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:32 44f3776135de48339762aaa6334d0215
msgid "``Bluetooth --> Bluedriod Enable --> Use dynamic memory allocation in BT/BLE stack.``"
msgstr "``Bluetooth --> Bluedriod Enable --> Use dynamic memory allocation in BT/BLE stack.``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:33 fe965edf2bc0425c89868448c1716489
msgid "``Bluetooth --> Blutooth controller --> BLE full scan feature supported.``"
msgstr "``Bluetooth --> Blutooth controller --> BLE full scan feature supported.``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:34 efd2b3300d7f4e979630c50c61f8d3c6
msgid "``Wi-Fi --> Software controls Wi-Fi/Bluetooth coexistence --> Wi-Fi``"
msgstr "``Wi-Fi --> Software controls Wi-Fi/Bluetooth coexistence --> Wi-Fi``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:39 8b17505e17654523bd1c98f3c5e2eaa3
msgid "ESP32 支持 16MB 的 External Flash 和 8MB 的 External PSRAM 共存吗？"
msgstr "Does ESP32 support coexistence of 16 MB External Flash and 8 MB External PSRAM?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:41 e828d20468e54952a404bdc0b93d95e2
msgid "ESP32 可以支持 16MB 的 External Flash 和 8MB 的 External PSRAM 共存使用。"
msgstr "ESP32 supports using 16 MB External Flash and 8 MB External PSRAM together."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:46 23383725700a4db7898ababf4ae385de
msgid "ESP32 Wi-Fi Mesh 和 BLE Mesh 可以同时支持吗？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 Wi-Fi Mesh and BLE Mesh be supported at the same time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:48 8b17e976c1bb407ca878dcab33177681
msgid "不支持，补充一点：ESP32 Wi-Fi Mesh 和 BLE 可以同时支持，或者 ESP32 Wi-Fi STA 模式和 BLE Mesh 可以同时支持。"
msgstr "No. To add, ESP32 Wi-Fi Mesh and BLE can be supported at the same time, or ESP32 Wi-Fi STA mode and BLE Mesh can be supported at the same time."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:53 6714ff5136c046ba9dc09d2c7ceadccb
msgid "ESP32 蓝牙和 WI-FI 能否同时使用？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 Bluetooth and Wi-Fi be used at the same time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:55 6460f06fbd124dbb816cf64d51b5d8ef
msgid "ESP32 的 Wi-Fi 和蓝牙可共存，但需要分时控制，可在 menuconfig 中使能 Wi-Fi 和蓝牙共存设置。如下："
msgstr "ESP32 Wi-Fi and Bluetooth can coexist, but time-division control is required. You can enable the Wi-Fi and Bluetooth coexistence setting in menuconfig as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:56 caf9f36b3b674eb2bff02ff061502d9b
msgid "``menuconfig -> Component config -> Wi-Fi -> Software controls WiFi/Bluetooth coexistence （Enable）``"
msgstr "``menuconfig -> Component config -> Wi-Fi -> Software controls WiFi/Bluetooth coexistence （Enable）``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:61 2e94dfcc422e47c2a9aec18848a28120
msgid "ble 和 a2dp 共存，进入 ble 扫描的时候音频数据接收会丢失、卡顿怎么解决？"
msgstr "When BLE and A2DP coexist, audio data reception is lost or stutters when BLE scanning starts. How can this be resolved?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:63 38b4a0d7674644f49e3729c8735870de
msgid "降低BLE扫描的占空比"
msgstr "Reduce the duty cycle of BLE scanning."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:64 6e0fdb5a4b9d47af9ce002a4d1349cb8
msgid "使用 ringbuf 缓存音频数据"
msgstr "Use a ringbuf to cache audio data."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:69 f839ae6b86d64586847d4c7456e01c67
msgid "ESP32 的网口 （LAN8720） 与 WIFI （WIFI-AP） 能否共存？"
msgstr "Can the ESP32 Ethernet port (LAN8720) and Wi-Fi (Wi-Fi AP) coexist?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:71 8ca2054d2bf24e04897e175f5e70a065
msgid "可以共存的。将两个连接的检测事件写成一个就可以实现共存。"
msgstr "They can coexist. Coexistence can be implemented by writing the detection events of the two connections into one event handler."

#~ msgid ":link_to_translation:`en:[English]`"
#~ msgstr ""
